Thereâ€™s hopefully nothing surprising going on here. Weâ€™re using semantic-ui-css for some styling, as well as a couple of styles of our own.

Then, in the table body weâ€™re iterating over the array of employees that we are passing in from app.js and outputting their details to a table.

